{"tid":1497563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這個政權不配——來自義務律師團隊","createTime":"2019-08-23T04:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T04:40:25.000Z","uid":294596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7542bcd4c4ebbb381382f8b7b4bda2e2a8afbc1d","tid":1497563,"uid":294596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其中一位被捕者，跟家弟同齡，才剛中學畢業。他看來十分虛弱，而當向他問及被捕時的情況，他有點欲語還休。我理解到他對外面看守着的警員有避忌，故趨前聽他耳語，他輕訴：「我是前線。」然後開始怔怔落淚。我感受到他的落淚並不是後悔，終究是受驚過度了。<br />\n當刻，我很想很想抱抱身材瘦弱、上了孖葉、帶傷的他。只想抱抱，緊緊的抱。但我只能為他抺淚。所有言語，在這刻都是蒼白的。我在心裡默唸：<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「對不起，謝謝你。」</span></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23041/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-23041/%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E4%B8%8D%E9%85%8D?fbclid=IwAR322jwoJTQqeP67kNTsEiKEtuWwWZaYSk-aixw9t8r2eb2mLWFC8aJ6s70\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23041%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-23041%2F%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25AC%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2585%258D%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR322jwoJTQqeP67kNTsEiKEtuWwWZaYSk-aixw9t8r2eb2mLWFC8aJ6s70&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1a0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=3021eea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23041/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-23041/%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E4%B8%8D%E9%85%8D?fbclid=IwAR322jwoJTQqeP67kNTsEiKEtuWwWZaYSk-aixw9t8r2eb2mLWFC8aJ6s70</a>"},{"pid":"bba0dacb8f56ad6063818c4d38da7091f239dcbb","tid":1497563,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"colo